data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled 1,842 sq ft, 4bed/3bath home, just minutes away from IB Pier and IB Navy base. Nestled in a family-friendly neighborhood, this residence offers a low maintenance landscape. Inside has beautiful updated floors, a fully remodeled kitchen with all SS, porcelain backsplash. The living room is open and bright with plenty of space for entertaining or just relaxing. 1 Bedroom and full bath on the main floor perfect for a live-in nanny or granny. Spacious 2 car garage with laundry located inside. Upstairs, you find find three remodeled bedrooms, including a primary suite with an exquisite master bath his and hers sinks. The backyard is a private with low maintenance turf all around. Additional upgrades include solar system, A/C unit, vivent home security system, LED recessed lighting, garage, covered parking w/ electric charging. Close to the ocean, schools, parks, shopping and more!
